      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a decent start, but it's a bit generic. I need to go deeper into the actual philosophy for my post. Can you specifically outline the libertarian or anarcho-capitalist arguments regarding 'digital sovereignty' and why they believe state intervention is inherently illegitimate in a virtual space?",
